codex
The D3D9 register map is explicit: dot3 diffuse is c1 and specular is c2, with alphaFadeOpacity aliased to c2.a in the shader-builder map. That makes the D3D11 source divergence very tight: the RGB is supposed to come from light colors, but the two alpha channels are not.
